Description
===========

Nucleus is another RSS news reader project.

Project Details
===============

Structure Overview
------------------

/nucleus-web - contains web portion of Nucleus project;
/nucleus-web/.etc - contains miscellaneous files, including mockups, sample apps and prototypes, todos, etc.;

Project Naming Conventions
--------------------------

* Please follow ex-Sun Java naming conventions.
* JavaDocs for tricky parts.

Libraries, Frameworks And Tools
-------------------------------

* Spring and Spring MVC for middleware layer;
* JPA for backend + Hibernate?;
* JSP for frontend:
    * JQuery + plugins;
    * Twitter Bootstrap;
    * AngularJS;

* Jackson serializer for JSON data + Dozer for mapping object-to-object.

* RSS ops:
    * ROME;


HTML Sanitizer
--------------

https://code.google.com/p/owasp-java-html-sanitizer/source/browse/trunk/src/tests/org/owasp/html/HtmlPolicyBuilderTest.java
http://owasp-java-html-sanitizer.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/distrib/javadoc/org/owasp/html/Sanitizers.html

Milestones
----------

M1
^^

M110 - User accounts registration.
M120 - Reader pane with feeds and navigation.
M130 - Import/export functionality.
M140 - Settings pane.
M150 - Welcome screen

M2
^^

M210 - Feeds ranking.
M220 - Full text search and indexing.